		<title>Is Writing &#8220;The End&#8221; a Bad Idea?&#8212;A Reader&#8217;s Question</title>
		<link>http://theeditorsblog.net/2014/09/17/is-writing-the-end-a-bad-idea-a-readers-question/</link>
		<comments>http://theeditorsblog.net/2014/09/17/is-writing-the-end-a-bad-idea-a-readers-question/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2014 14:35:23 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Fiction Editor Beth Hill]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[A Reader Asks...]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Recommendations]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[format]]></category>
